title: Photos: Oklahoma Sooners dominate early and often in 55-0 shutout against Kansas State
text: Oct 17, 2015; Manhattan, KS, USA; Oklahoma Sooners running back Joe Mixon (25) runs the ball from Kansas State Wildcats linebacker Will Davis (35) and defensive back Nate Jackson (24) on his way to a touchdown in a 55-0 win at Bill Snyder Family Football Stadium.
